channel.name: BBC One NL
channel.title: Homes Under the Hammer
channel.desc: A detached house in Whittlesey in Cambridgeshire, a property in Tunstall in Stoke and a terraced house full of period features in Ipswich in Suffolk are all sold at online auctions. Tommy and Jacqui meet the new owners and learn about their plans to make some money from their investments.
